name: YouTube Late 2010-Early 2011 [BROKEN]
description:
A very shoddy thing that makes YouTube look older.

Currently works on 1920x1080 displays only.

Tutorial: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XI82lRfwV_0

Links to things:
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/violentmonkey/jinjaccalgkegednnccohejagnlnfdag
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/youtube-redux/mdgdgieddpndgjlmeblhjgljejejkikf
http://7kttube.tk/downloads/3/7ktTube-290
https://greasyfork.org/en/scripts/405614-youtube-polymer-engine-fixes

additional_info:
8/10/21 | V1.0.0: 

Released the Userstyle.
--------------------------------

8/10/21 | V1.0.0-b: 

Fixed 'Show More' button not displaying.
------------------------------------------------------

8/10/21 | V1.0.0-c: 

Completely fixed 'Show More' button not displaying.
---------------------------------------------------------------------

8/12/21 | V1.0.1: 

{[BEFORE YOU UPDATE]}

Watch this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ODWcuxlDS1s

[Changes]

Player now looks as it did in June 2011.

Likes, dislikes and views area looks a lot better now.

The big gap under the player has been removed.

Player size has been reduced for greater accuracy.

'SHOW MORE' text at the bottom of the description is no longer in all caps.

'SHOW MORE' button now has a gradient. No dark mode support yet.

Changed 'Upload' button to only text.

Fixed the wrong-looking button.

[Issues]

I have yet to find a fix for the large spinner.

The annotations button uses the same icon as the settings button.

The progress bar does not go all the way to the right.

The header does not fill out the top of the page when in theater mode.
--------------------------------------------------------------------

8/27/21 | V1.0.1-b: 

{[BEFORE YOU UPDATE]}

Watch this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g7satgqrJOU

[Changes]

The large spinner has been fixed in recent versions of YouTube Redux.

'Show more' button now has dark mode support.

'Like' and 'Dislike' buttons now have dark mode support.

'Save' button now has dark mode support.

'Share' button now has dark mode support.

'Report' and 'Open transcript' button now has dark mode support.

'Upload' button is no longer only text due to the icon showing through.

[Issues]

I have yet to find a fix for the theater mode header issue.

The 'Report' and 'Open transcript' button's previous icon is showing.

The spinner is not centered.
---------------------------------------------------------------------
